      <div class="credential-column">
        <ol class="credential-steps">
          <li class="credential-step" data-animate="credential-step">
            <span class="credential-step-index">01</span>
            <div class="credential-step-body">
              <h3>State Commissioned</h3>
              <p>Active Pennsylvania Notary Public maintaining jurisdictional training and regulatory updates.</p>
              <ul class="credential-step-list">
                <li>Ongoing continuing education each renewal cycle</li>
                <li>Audit-ready digital journal and secure seal custody</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="credential-step" data-animate="credential-step">
            <span class="credential-step-index">02</span>
            <div class="credential-step-body">
              <h3>NNA Certified Signing Agent</h3>
              <p>Yearly background screening, loan signing certification, and lender-specific protocols mastered.</p>
              <ul class="credential-step-list">
                <li>TRID, HELOC, reverse, and refinance script proficiency</li>
                <li>Secure scan-backs, packaging, and courier drop-off handled</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="credential-step" data-animate="credential-step">
            <span class="credential-step-index">03</span>
            <div class="credential-step-body">
              <h3>Bonded & Insured</h3>
              <p>$100,000 E&O policy plus industry bonding to protect every client, lender, and title partner.</p>
              <ul class="credential-step-list">
                <li>Dual ID verification and compliance-ready audit trail</li>
                <li>Equipment sanitized and sealed between appointments</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </li>
